		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Man, you should build a tracer (logger) that shows the amount of emulated cycles per frame and the main events (VBlank flag rising, 2002 clearing, frame start etc). This way, you will see where your emu is failing, or else, it's hard.

		

